Overview
-----
Optimizing code by writing efficient function using React wisely.
Get into code splitting

Big picture on how to think about code in order to be as efficient as possible.
Often overlooked, as people focus on just getting it to work.

Talk about progressive web apps. A recent idea of trying to make web app as close to native mobile apps as possible.
Helps with app working offline and in slow connection areas, and submitting to app stores.